---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Partner Conversations - SkanPay"
  description="SkanPay helps payment apps, mobile wallets, loyalty platforms, and commerce partners explore their role in QR checkout."
  activePath="/partners/"
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Partners</p>
    <h1>Define the app handoff before checkout goes live</h1>
    <p>Partner conversations focus on what the customer app handles, what the store sees, and where the transaction boundary sits.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="grid three">
      <article class="card route-card">
        <span>Payment app</span>
        <h3>Customer approval</h3>
        <p>Show the customer the merchant, amount, and approval action in a trusted app experience.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card route-card">
        <span>Merchant</span>
        <h3>Store confirmation</h3>
        <p>Return a readable result so counter staff know whether to complete, retry, or cancel the sale.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card route-card">
        <span>Integration</span>
        <h3>Defined boundaries</h3>
        <p>Clarify request format, status handling, timeout behavior, and support responsibilities.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Partner path</p>
      <h2>Use BeamCash to make the conversation concrete.</h2>
      <p>The demo shows the checkout experience before deeper partner-specific requirements are discussed.</p>
    </div>
    <a class="button secondary" href="/beamcash-demo/">View BeamCash Demo</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
